    "(13).Chaser Fish: In the entire goatfish group, a chaser fish is available which initiates hunting.",
    "Here, the chaser fish are selected based on the fitness value.",
    "In every cluster, the particle has a superior fitness value which is close to the final solution.",
    "While hunting is executed, the prey escapes under the corals and then hides in the crevices through a random walk.",
    "The mathematical representation of the chaser fish's new location is presented in Eq."
  ]
